column2: "Yo, are you ready to die yet? It's just a joke, you don't need to look so scared."
"But really you're a lot like Zeno, doing needless stuff all of the time. Makes me want to kill you more and more."
"Not quite. He's just started to scrape the surface, but you're not quite there yet."
"What a good little brat you are. You still don't get it yet."
"Why don't you try it just once? Going beyond that boundary you've set for yourself. It's fun!"
"If you can't understand what I'm saying then that just makes me want to kill you more. Come on Sheena, let's go."
